
ASSIGNMENT 1 PYTHON
1.	Program to enter length and breadth of a rectangle and calculate area and perimeter of the rectangle
PROGRAM
l=input("Enter the length: ")
b=input("Enter the breadth: ")
a=l*b
p=2*(l+b)
print("Area of rectangle is %s") %(a)
print("Perimeter of rectangle is %s") %(p)

OUTPUT:
 
2.	WPP TO ENTER RADIUS OF CIRCLE AND CALCULATE AREA AND CIRCUMFERENCE OF CIRCLE
PROGRAM
