c=2*3.14*r
print " "
print("Area of circle is %s") %(a)
print("Circumference of circle is %s") %(c)

OUTPUT:
 


3.	WPP TO ENTER VALUE IN CENTIMETRE AND CONVERT IT TO METER AND KILOMETRE
PROGRAM
